  m_Text: "<b>Goal</b>\nPass checkpoints in order\nFinish all laps\nAvoid fluids\nEmbody the spirit of fast\n\n\n<b>Keyboard controls:</b>\n<b>WASD keys</b>: Go fast\n<b>Arrow keys</b>: Look around fast\n<b>Space</b>: Jump fast\n<b>Shift</b>: Brake fast\n<b>R</b>: Respawn fast\n\n\n<b>Joystick controls</b>:\n<b>Left axis</b>: Go fast\n<b>Right axis</b>: Look around fast\n<b>A</b>: Jump fast\n<b>B</b>: Brake fast\n<b>Y</b>: Respawn fast\n\n\nPress <b>F1</b>\n(<b>Select/Back/View</b> on controller)\nto hide this"
